{"tid":901150,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人生就係一個超鏈結","createTime":"2018-11-13T19:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T19:07:14.000Z","uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1970ebff6ba99f2a855ec12d77a6b421f1cfe8a4","tid":901150,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T19:05:19.000Z","msg":"世界好多野，都係偶然發生，唔係做咩就有既定結果。<br />\n<br />\n點解地球存在左46億年，會係2000萬年中間，突然出現98% 既地球物種。打個譬如， 00：00- 2130 之間有6分鐘出現物種大爆炸。 <br />\n<br />\n讀邊間大學，同邊個結婚，番咩工，同邊個創業，有邊樣係係自己規劃之下？ <br />\n<br />\n人生唔再係一本書，現今社會變得太快，你所規劃所準備既，係未來都會轉變成另一個趨勢。internet&gt;淘寶&gt;騰訊&gt;big data&gt;ai。 我地能夠做既，唔係由零開始，慢慢研究未來發展趨勢再起步，而係無時無刻裝備自己，機會埋身就take action。"},{"pid":"e2d6dee96f105fd63688068bcb8bef524dd9bf9d","tid":901150,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T19:06:20.000Z","msg":"紫lin  <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf2302f638bbf4621a550918463505de9ff024f","tid":901150,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2d6dee96f105fd63688068bcb8bef524dd9bf9d","tid":901150,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T19:06:20.000Z","msg":"紫lin  <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T19:07:14.000Z","msg":"負皮d 咩"}]}